body_html:
thansk! @keyongyu I follow your step.it works!
first,I compile the build_all_android.sh,then I got the same error. then I remove nsync builds armeabi-v7a.android.c++11 folder ,update the compile_nsync.sh, cover build_all_android.sh about dowloading and front of nsync. Finally compile build_all_android.sh again.here are my bash.
sudo NDK_ROOT=/Users/a1707001/android-ndk-r14b sh tensorflow/contrib/makefile/build_all_android.sh
btw my tensorflow version is v1.4.0 ,ndk version is r14b.
